bg tatsu-one-half tatsu-column-image-none tatsu-column-effect-none  tatsu-HknzzPAHI\" data-animation=\"fadeIn\"   data-parallax-speed=\"0\" style=\"\"><div class=\"tatsu-column-inner \" ><div class=\"tatsu-column-pad-wrap\"><div class=\"tatsu-column-pad\" ><div  class=\"tatsu-module tatsu-text-block-wrap tatsu-S1hjMw0BL  \"><div class=\"tatsu-text-inner tatsu-align-center  clearfix\" data-animation=\"fadeIn\"  ><style>.tatsu-S1hjMw0BL.tatsu-text-block-wrap .tatsu-text-inner{width: 100%;text-align: left;}.tatsu-S1hjMw0BL.tatsu-text-block-wrap{margin: 30px 0px 30px 0px;}<\/style>\n<h6><em>&#8220;Their caring attitude and attention to detail are a welcome relief when going through a difficult time.&#8221;<\/em><\/h6>\n<p>I first learned of Home Comfort Care when searching for a caregiver for my boss, who needed assistance following surgery. His physician\u2019s office recommended Home Comfort Care as a perfect fit for our needs.\u00a0 We ultimately employed a caregiver from Home Comfort Care and found the service to be terrific. The caregiver\u2019s attention to my boss was first-rate and the family spoke very highly of the company.<\/p>\n<p>However, it was not until my own family was in need for a caregiver that I really had a chance to work with Cheryl. My dad was placed in in-home hospice and things became more difficult for my family to manage alone. Based on my earlier experience with Home Comfort Care, I did not hesitate to contact Cheryl. Within a week, we had a plan in place and a caregiver staying with my dad for eight to ten hours per night.\u00a0<\/p>\n<p>Not only are the caregivers providing much needed physical care for my dad, we also have the added expertise of Cheryl\u2019s RN skills. I have found Cheryl to be very hands-on with the caregivers during the evening should they have any questions. She is also very responsive to my family and keeps in regular communication.\u00a0<\/p>\n<p>In conclusion, I would not hesitate to recommend Home Comfort Care for you or a loved one. Their caring attitude and attention to detail are a welcome relief when going through a difficult time. You can rest easy knowing that you are in good hands.<\/p>\n<p>Nancy G.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class = \"tatsu-column-bg-image-wrap\"><div class = \"tatsu-column-bg-image\" ><\/div><\/div><\/div><style>.tatsu-row > .tatsu-HknzzPAHI.tatsu-column{width: 50%;}.tatsu-HknzzPAHI.tatsu-column > .tatsu-column-inner > .tatsu-column-overlay{mix-blend-mode: none;}.tatsu-HknzzPAHI > .tatsu-column-inner > .tatsu-top-divider{z-index: 9999;}.tatsu-HknzzPAHI > .tatsu-column-inner > .tatsu-bottom-divider{z-index: 9999;}.tatsu-HknzzPAHI > .tatsu-column-inner > .tatsu-left-divider{z-index: 9999;}.tatsu-HknzzPAHI > .tatsu-column-inner > .tatsu-right-divider{z-index: 9999;}.tatsu-HknzzPAHI.tatsu-column{transform: translate3d(0px,0px, 0);}@media only screen and (max-width:1377px) {.tatsu-row > .tatsu-HknzzPAHI.tatsu-column{width: 50%;}}@media only screen and (min-width:768px) and (max-width: 1024px) {.tatsu-row > .tatsu-HknzzPAHI.tatsu-column{width: 50%;}}@media only screen and (max-width: 767px) {.tatsu-row > .tatsu-HknzzPAHI.tatsu-column{width: 100%;}}<\/style><\/div><div  class=\"tatsu-column  tatsu-column-no-bg tatsu-one-half tatsu-column-image-none tatsu-column-effect-none  tatsu-BJenzzDRSI\" data-animation=\"fadeIn\"   data-parallax-speed=\"0\" style=\"\"><div class=\"tatsu-column-inner \" ><div class=\"tatsu-column-pad-wrap\"><div class=\"tatsu-column-pad\" ><div  class=\"tatsu-module tatsu-text-block-wrap tatsu-SyXsZP0SI  \"><div class=\"tatsu-text-inner tatsu-align-center  clearfix\" data-animation=\"fadeIn\"  ><style>.tatsu-SyXsZP0SI.tatsu-text-block-wrap .tatsu-text-inner{width: 100%;text-align: left;}.tatsu-SyXsZP0SI.tatsu-text-block-wrap{margin: 30px 0px 55px 0px;}<\/style>\n<h6><em>&#8220;I am very happy with the care I have received from this company and their employee&#8230;a\u00a0wonderful caregiver!&#8221;<\/em><\/h6>\n<p>The following is a recommendation for Home Comfort Care. I am very happy with the care I have received from this company and their employee, Maureen. Cheryl Linderman, a registered nurse is the owner\/operator, has been very informative and able to adapt to my requirements.\u00a0Maureen is a wonderful caregiver! She is very friendly and personable and is a great cleaner. She seems to anticipate what needs to be done without being asked. I enjoy her company and conversation.<\/p>\n<p>Donna B.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><div  class=\"tatsu-module tatsu-text-block-wrap tatsu-r1mAovArL  \"><div class=\"tatsu-text-inner tatsu-align-center  clearfix\" data-animation=\"fadeIn\"  ><style>.tatsu-r1mAovArL.tatsu-text-block-wrap .tatsu-text-inner{width: 100%;text-align: left;}.tatsu-r1mAovArL.tatsu-text-block-wrap{margin: -5px 0px 50px 0px;}<\/style>\n<h6><em>&#8220;What an amazing team of nurses who took care of my father&#8221;<\/em><\/h6>\n<p>I cannot express to you how thankful we are for Home Comfort Care. What an amazing team of nurses who took care of my father. My father was dying of brain cancer, and we decided to hire HCC to take care of him 24 hours a day. The personal care he had was amazing. They made sure he was not in any pain, administered his medication, sat with him, changed his positioning, worked with hospice, cleaned him, rubbed his head, and cried with us during his final days. I highly recommend HCC, and if anyone would like to talk with me about my experience please call me at 248-686-6888.<\/p>\n<p>Heather L. and\u00a0Linda C.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><div  class=\"tatsu-module tatsu-text-block-wrap tatsu-HJBv6_jPI  \"><div class=\"tatsu-text-inner tatsu-align-center  clearfix\" data-animation=\"fadeIn\"  ><style>.tatsu-HJBv6_jPI.tatsu-text-block-wrap .tatsu-text-inner{width: 100%;text-align: left;}.tatsu-HJBv6_jPI.tatsu-text-block-wrap{margin: -5px 0px 50px 0px;}<\/style>\n<h6><em>Thank you<\/em><\/h6>\n<p>The ride to my doctor turned out just fine. Maureen was helpful and I enjoyed meeting her. \u00a0Thank you.<\/p>\n<p>Marylyn H.<\/p>\n<p>\u00a0<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class = \"tatsu-column-bg-image-wrap\"><div class = \"tatsu-column-bg-image\" ><\/div><\/div><\/div><style>.tatsu-row > .tatsu-BJenzzDRSI.tatsu-column{width: 50%;}.tatsu-BJenzzDRSI.tatsu-column > .tatsu-column-inner > .tatsu-column-overlay{mix-blend-mode: none;}.tatsu-BJenzzDRSI > .tatsu-column-inner > .tatsu-top-divider{z-index: 9999;}.tatsu-BJenzzDRSI > .tatsu-column-inner > .tatsu-bottom-divider{z-index: 9999;}.tatsu-BJenzzDRSI > .tatsu-column-inner > .tatsu-left-divider{z-index: 9999;}.tatsu-BJenzzDRSI > .tatsu-column-inner > .tatsu-right-divider{z-index: 9999;}.tatsu-BJenzzDRSI.tatsu-column{transform: translate3d(0px,0px, 0);}@media only screen and (max-width:1377px) {.tatsu-row > .tatsu-BJenzzDRSI.tatsu-column{width: 50%;}}@media only screen and (min-width:768px) and (max-width: 1024px) {.tatsu-row > .tatsu-BJenzzDRSI.tatsu-column{width: 50%;}}@media only screen and (max-width: 767px) {.tatsu-row > .tatsu-BJenzzDRSI.tatsu-column{width: 100%;}}<\/style><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"tatsu-section-background-wrap\"><div class = \"tatsu-section-background\" ><\/div><\/div><style>.tatsu-rJ-Q9WPRSI .tatsu-section-pad{padding: 0px 0px 90px 0px;}.tatsu-rJ-Q9WPRSI > .tatsu-bottom-divider{z-index: 9999;}.tatsu-rJ-Q9WPRSI > .tatsu-top-divider{z-index: 9999;}<\/style><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p><a href=\"https:\/\/homecomfortcare.org\/client-referrals\/\" class=\"more-link style3-button\">Read More<\/a><\/p>","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v18.2 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Client Referrals - Home Comfort Care<\/title>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large,